<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> Badrul M. Sarwar, George Karypis, Joseph A. Konstan, John Riedl: Item-based collaborative filtering recommendation algorithms. WWW 2001: 285-295</li>
<li id="cite_note-lemire2005-2">^ <a href="#cite_ref-lemire2005_2-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-lemire2005_2-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-lemire2005_2-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> Daniel Lemire, Anna Maclachlan, <a href="http://arxiv.org/abs/cs/0702144" class="external text" title="http://arxiv.org/abs/cs/0702144" rel="nofollow">Slope One Predictors for Online Rating-Based Collaborative Filtering</a>, In SIAM Data Mining (SDM'05), Newport Beach, California, April 21-23, 2005.</li>
